-- German Bunds Extend Decline as Draghi Says ECB Has Bond Plan
-- B y   E m m a   C h a r l t o n
-- 2012-09-06T12:34:57Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-09-06/german-bunds-extend-decline-as-draghi-says-ecb-has-bond-plan.html
German government bonds extended
their decline after European Central Bank President  Mario Draghi 
said the central bank had decided on the modalities of its bond-
purchase program.  Ten-year bund yields advanced seven basis points to 1.55
percent at 1:33 p.m. London time.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Emma Charlton in London at 
